Sebastian Vettel will 'get p****d tonight' to celebrate his victory at the Malaysian Grand Prix.

The 27-year-old German produced a stunning performance to win in his Ferrari ahead of Mercedes pair Lewis Hamilton and Nico Rosberg at the Sepang International Circuit.

The four-time world champion was visibly emotional on the podium after enduring a torrid 2014 season, his final year with Red Bull before switching to Ferrari over the winter.

